lead_paragraph: Joao Plata and Javier Morales scored on well-placed shots early in the second half and Real Salt Lake beat the Philadelphia Union 2-1 on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Plato, Morales Rally Real Salt Lake Past Union 2-1
